      "source_repo": "coderaiser/putout",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\ud83d\udc0a  Pluggable and configurable JavaScript Linter, code transformer and formatter with superpowers \ud83d\udcaa: built-in support of js, jsx, ts, markdown, yaml, toml, json and ignore. Write declarative codemods in a simplest possible way \ud83d\ude0f"
